Class EventView

java.lang.Object
com.example.lotto649.AbstractClasses.AbstractView
com.example.lotto649.Views.EventView
public class EventView extends AbstractView
EventView is responsible for observing changes in the EventModel and updating the corresponding EventFragment with the latest event details.
